>查找</strong> 并报告 WordPress 核心软件中的错误。','If you do code, or want to learn how, you can contribute technically in numerous ways:'=>'如果您编写代码，或者想学习如何编写代码，您可以通过多种方式做出技术贡献：','Code-based contribution'=>'基于代码的贡献','<strong>Explore</strong> ways to reduce the environmental impact of websites.'=>'<strong>探索</strong> 减少数百万个网站对环境影响的方法。','<strong>Edit</strong> videos and add captions to WordPress.tv.'=>'<strong>编辑</strong> 视频并向 WordPress.tv 添加字幕。','<strong>Lend</strong> your creative imagination to the WordPress UI design.'=>'<strong>发挥</strong> 您的创意想象力到 WordPress UI 设计中。','<strong>Organize</strong> or participate in local Meetups and WordCamps.'=>'<strong>组织</strong> 或参加本地 WordPress 聚会和 WordCamp。','<strong>Curate</strong> submissions or take photos for the Photo Directory.'=>'<strong>策划</strong> 提交内容或为 WordPress 照片目录拍摄照片。','<strong>Promote</strong> the WordPress project to your community.'=>'<strong>推广</strong> 向您的社区 WordPress 项目。','<strong>Create</strong> and improve WordPress educational materials.'=>'<strong>创建</strong>并改进 WordPress 教育材料。','<strong>Translate</strong> WordPress into your local language.'=>'<strong>翻译</strong> 将 WordPress 带入您的本地语言。','<strong>Write</strong> or improve documentation for WordPress.'=>'<strong>编写</strong> 或改进 WordPress 文档。','<strong>Share</strong> your knowledge in the WordPress support forums.'=>'<strong>分享</strong> 您的知识在 WordPress 支持论坛。','WordPress may thrive on technical contributions, but you don&#8217;t have to code to contribute. Here are some of the ways you can make an impact without writing a single line of code:'=>'WordPress 可能会因技术贡献而蓬勃发展，但您不必编写代码即可做出贡献。以下是一些无需编写任何代码即可产生影响的方法：','No-code contribution'=>'无代码贡献','Grow your network and make friends.'=>'拓展您的网络并结交朋友。','Apply your skills or learn new ones.'=>'运用您的技能或学习新技能。','Be part of a global open source community.'=>'成为全球开源社区的一部分。','Join the diverse WordPress contributor community and connect with other people who are passionate about maintaining a free and open web.'=>'加入 WordPress 贡献者社区，并与热衷于维护自由开放网络的其他人联系。','Do you use WordPress for work, for personal projects, or even just for fun? You can help shape the long-term success of the open source project that powers millions of websites around the world.'=>'您使用 WordPress 是为了工作、个人项目，还是只是为了好玩？您可以帮助塑造为全球数百万网站提供支持的开源项目的长期成功。','Be the future of WordPress'=>'成为 WordPress 的未来','<a href="%1$s">Learn WordPress</a> is a free resource for new and experienced WordPress users. Learn is stocked with how-to videos on using various features in WordPress, <a href="%2$s">interactive workshops</a> for exploring topics in-depth, and lesson plans for diving deep into specific areas of WordPress.'=>'<a href="%1$s">学习 WordPress</a> 是为 WordPress 新用户和经验丰富的用户提供的免费资源。学习包含有关使用 WordPress 中的各种功能的操作视频、用于深入探索主题的<a href="%2$s">互动活动</a>以及用于深入了解 WordPress 特定领域的课程计划。','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/forums/">Support forums</a>'=>'<a href="https://cn.wordpress.org/support/forums/">支持论坛</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/appearance-widgets-screen-classic-editor/">Documentation on Widgets</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/appearance-widgets-screen-classic-editor/">小工具文档</a>','<strong>View</strong> takes you to a public author archive which lists all the posts published by the user.'=>'<strong>查看</strong> 带您前往一个公开的作者归档页面，其中列出了由此用户发表的全部文章。','<strong>Download file</strong> downloads the original media file to your device.'=>'<strong>下载文件</strong> 将下载原始媒体文件到您的设备上。','site editor title tagEditor'=>'编辑器','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/plugins-themes-auto-updates/">Documentation on Auto-updates</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/plugins-themes-auto-updates/">关于自动更新的文档</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customize-date-and-time-format/">Documentation on date and time formatting</a>.'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customize-date-and-time-format/">关于日期和时间格式的文档</a>。','You can set the language, and WordPress will automatically download and install the translation files (available if your filesystem is writable).'=>'您可以设置语言，WordPress 将会自动下载并安装翻译文件（如果您的文件系统可写）。','If you want site visitors to be able to register themselves, check the membership box. If you want the site administrator to register every new user, leave the box unchecked. In either case, you can set a default user role for all new users.'=>'如果您希望站点的访问者能够自行注册账号，请勾选「成员资格」复选框。如果您希望站点管理员来注册每一个新用户，请将此复选框留空。无论是哪种情况，您都可以为所有新用户设置默认的用户角色。','Both WordPress URL and site URL can start with either %1$s or %2$s. A URL starting with %2$s requires an SSL certificate, so be sure that you have one before changing to %2$s. With %2$s, a padlock will appear next to the address in the browser address bar. Both %2$s and the padlock signal that your site meets some basic security requirements, which can build trust with your visitors and with search engines.'=>'WordPress URL 和站点 URL 都可以以 %1$s 或 %2$s 开头。以 %2$s 开头的 URL 要求 SSL 证书，请确保您在将开头变更为 %2$s 之前，已经安装了对应该地址的 SSL 证书。以 %2$s 开头的 URL，会在浏览器地址栏靠近地址的地方显示一个锁头图标。 %2$s 和锁头图标都表明您的站点已经满足了一些基本的安全要求，意味着您的访客和搜索引擎都可以与您的站点建立可信连接。','Though the terms refer to two different concepts, in practice, they can be the same address or different. For example, you can have the core WordPress installation files in the root directory (<code>https://example.com</code>), in which case the two URLs would be the same. Or the <a href="%s">WordPress files can be in a subdirectory</a> (<code>https://example.com/wordpress</code>). In that case, the WordPress URL and the site URL would be different.'=>'尽管这两个项目代表了两个不同的概念，但在实践中它们可以是同一个地址也可以是不同的地址。例如，您可以将 WordPress 核心安装文件放在根目录中（<code>https://example.com</code>），在这种情况下两个 URL 将会保持一致。或者<a href="%s">WordPress 也可以在子目录中</a>（<code>https://example.com/wordpress</code>）。在这种情况下，WordPress URL 和站点 URL 将会不同。','Two terms you will want to know are the WordPress URL and the site URL. The WordPress URL is where the core WordPress installation files are, and the site URL is the address a visitor uses in the browser to go to your site.'=>'您需要了解的两个概念是 WordPress URL 与站点 URL。 WordPress URL 是 WordPress 核心安装文件的位置，而站点 URL 是当访客访问您站点时候使用的地址。','RoboHash (Generated)'=>'RoboHash（自动生成）','site editor menu itemEditor'=>'编辑','Allow <a href="%s">trackbacks and pingbacks</a>'=>'允许 <a href="%s">Trackback 和 Pingback</a>','https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/assign-custom-fields/'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/assign-custom-fields/','https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/what-is-an-excerpt-classic-editor/'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/what-is-an-excerpt-classic-editor/','%s expects a non-empty string.'=>'%s 必须是一个非空的字符串。','The destination directory already exists and could not be removed.'=>'目标目录已经存在且无法移除。','The destination folder already exists.'=>'目标目录已存在。','The source and destination are the same.'=>'来源和目标相同。','https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/changing-file-permissions/'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/changing-file-permissions/','Expand or collapse the elements by clicking on their headings, and arrange them by dragging their headings or by clicking on the up and down arrows.'=>'通过单击标题展开或折叠元素，并通过拖动标题或单击向上和向下箭头来排列它们。','Download &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'下载「%s」','The "%s" argument must be a non-empty string.'=>'「%s」参数必须是非空字符串。','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/write-posts-classic-editor/">Documentation on Writing and Editing Posts</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/write-posts-classic-editor/">撰写和编辑文章的文档</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/keyboard-shortcuts-classic-editor/#keyboard-shortcuts-for-comments">Documentation on Keyboard Shortcuts</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/keyboard-shortcuts-classic-editor/#keyboard-shortcuts-for-comments">键盘快捷键文档</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/understand-comment-spam/">Documentation on Comment Spam</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/understand-comment-spam/">垃圾评论文档</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customizer/">Documentation on Customizer</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customizer/">定制器文档</a>','https://wordpress.org/download/'=>'https://cn.wordpress.org/download/','This is the final release of WordPress %s'=>'这是 WordPress %s 的最终版本','Site Editor'=>'站点编辑器','<strong>Send password reset</strong> sends the user an email with a link to set a new password.'=>'<strong>发送密码重置</strong> 将向用户发送一封带有设置新密码链接的电子邮件。','https://developer.wordpress.org/apis/wp-config-php/#wp-environment-type'=>'https://developer.wordpress.org/apis/wp-config-php/#wp-environment-type','<strong>Copy URL</strong> copies the URL for the media file to your clipboard.'=>'<strong>复制 URL 到剪贴板</strong> 复制媒体文件的 URL 到您的剪贴板。','<strong>View</strong> will take you to a public display page for that file.'=>'<strong>查看</strong> 将带您到该文件的公开展示页面。','<strong>Delete Permanently</strong> will delete the file from the media library (as well as from any posts to which it is currently attached).'=>'<strong>永久删除</strong> 将从媒体库中删除该文件（以及任何附加了该文件的文章中）。','<strong>Edit</strong> takes you to a simple screen to edit that individual file&#8217;s metadata. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the media file name or thumbnail.'=>'<strong>编辑</strong> 会把您带到一个简单的页面来编辑单独文件的元数据。您也能通过点击文件名称或缩略图来进入这个页面。','Hovering over a row reveals action links that allow you to manage media items. You can perform the following actions:'=>'将光标悬停在列表中的某一行上，将显示操作链接使得您可以管理媒体项目。您可以执行以下操作:','themesBlock Themes'=>'区块主题','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/block-themes/">Documentation on Block Themes</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/block-themes/">区块主题文档</a>','Block themes'=>'区块主题','With a block theme, you can place and edit blocks without affecting your content by customizing or creating new templates.'=>'通过使用区块主题，您将能在不影响您的内容的情况下，通过自定义或新建模版来放置及编辑模块。','A block theme is a theme that uses blocks for all parts of a site including navigation menus, header, content, and site footer. These themes are built for the features that allow you to edit and customize all parts of your site.'=>'区块主题是一个可以在站点的所有部分包括导航菜单、页眉、内容以及站点页脚使用区块的主题。这些主题是为了使您能够编辑和定制您的整个站点的特性而设计的。','Recommended items are considered beneficial to your site, although not as important to prioritize as a critical issue, they may include improvements to things such as; Performance, user experience, and more.'=>'推荐改进项目是对您的站点有益处的项目，尽管其不像关键问题那样需要优先考虑，它们仍然包含对于如网站性能、用户体验等项目的改进。','Critical issues are items that may have a high impact on your sites performance or security, and resolving these issues should be prioritized.'=>'关键问题是那些可能对您的站点性能或安全有重大影响的项目，这些问题应当被优先解决。','The theme you are currently using is not compatible with the Site Editor.'=>'您目前使用的主题不支持站点编辑器。','Configuration rules for %s:'=>'%s 的配置规则：','Customize permalink structure by selecting available tags'=>'选择可用标签来自定义固定链接结构','Select the permalink structure for your website. Including the %s tag makes links easy to understand, and can help your posts rank higher in search engines.'=>'选择您的站点所要使用的固定链接结构。纳入 %s 标签能让链接更容易理解，也能帮助您的文章在搜索引擎中有更好的排名。','%s removed from permalink structure'=>'%s 已经从固定链接结构中删除','Site Health %s'=>'站点健康 %s','Theme Styles & Block Settings'=>'主题样式和区块设置','The minimum recommended version of PHP is %s.'=>'PHP 的最低建议版本为 %s。','PHP is one of the programming languages used to build WordPress. Newer versions of PHP receive regular security updates and may increase your site&#8217;s performance.'=>'PHP 是用于搭建 WordPress 的编程语言之一。较新版本的 PHP 能接受定期安全更新，也能提升您网站的性能。','Your site is running on an outdated version of PHP (%s), which soon will not be supported by WordPress. Ensure that PHP is updated on your server as soon as possible. Otherwise you will not be able to upgrade WordPress.'=>'您的站点正在运行过时版本的 PHP （%s），其很快将不被 WordPress 所支持。请确保尽快更新您服务器上的 PHP。否则您将无法升级 WordPress。','Your site is running on an outdated version of PHP (%s), which does not receive security updates and soon will not be supported by WordPress. Ensure that PHP is updated on your server as soon as possible. Otherwise you will not be able to upgrade WordPress.'=>'您的站点正在运行过时版本的 PHP （%s），其无法接收安全更新，而且很快将不被 WordPress 所支持。请确保尽快更新您服务器上的 PHP。否则您将无法升级 WordPress。','Persistent object cache'=>'持久对象缓存','Page cache'=>'页面缓存','You should use a persistent object cache'=>'您应该使用持久对象缓存','Your host appears to support the following object caching services: %s.'=>'您的主机似乎支持下列对象缓存服务：%s。','Your hosting provider can tell you if a persistent object cache can be enabled on your site.'=>'您的主机提供商可以告诉您是否可以在您的站点上启用持久对象存储。','A persistent object cache is not required'=>'持久对象缓存不是必须的','Learn more about persistent object caching.'=>'了解有关持久对象缓存的更多信息。','A persistent object cache makes your site&#8217;s database more efficient, resulting in faster load times because WordPress can retrieve your site&#8217;s content and settings much more quickly.'=>'持久对象存储可以提升您的站点数据库的执行效率，通过让 WordPress 更快地获取您站点的内容和设置以实现更短的加载时间。','A persistent object cache is being used'=>'正在使用一个持久对象缓存','https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/optimization/#persistent-object-cache'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/optimization/#persistent-object-cache','A page cache plugin was not detected.'=>'未检测到页面缓存插件。','A page cache plugin was detected.'=>'已检测到页面缓存插件。','There was %d client caching response header detected:'=>'检测到 %d 个客户端缓存响应标头：','No client caching response headers were detected.'=>'未检测到客户端缓存响应标头。','Median server response time was %1$s milliseconds. It should be less than the recommended %2$s milliseconds threshold.'=>'服务器响应时间的中位数是 %1$s 毫秒，其应当小于推荐的 %2$s 毫秒临界值。','Median server response time was %1$s milliseconds. This is less than the recommended %2$s milliseconds threshold.'=>'服务器响应时间的中位数是 %1$s 毫秒，小于推荐的 %2$s 毫秒临界值。','Server response time could not be determined. Verify that loopback requests are working.'=>'无法确定服务器响应时间。请确认环回请求是否正常工作。','Page cache is detected but the server response time is still slo