r-to-your-plugin/" target="_blank">learn more about how to add the Personal Data Exporter to a plugin here</a>.'=>'插件制作者可以<a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/plugins/privacy/adding-the-personal-data-exporter-to-your-plugin/" target="_blank">了解更多有关如何将个人数据导出器添加到插件的信息</a>。','Many plugins may collect or store personal data either in the WordPress database or remotely. Any Export Personal Data request should include data from plugins as well.'=>'许多插件可以在 WordPress 数据库中收集、存储个人数据，或通过远程方式收集、存储。任何导出个人数据请求都应该包括来自插件的数据。','If you are not sure, check the plugin documentation or contact the plugin author to see if the plugin collects data and if it supports the Data Exporter tool. This information may be available in the <a href="%s">Privacy Policy Guide</a>.'=>'如果不确定，请查看插件文档或与插件作者联系，以了解插件是否收集数据及是否支持个人数据导出器工具。此信息可在《<a href="%s">隐私政策指南</a>》中找到。','<strong>Comments</strong> &mdash; For user comments, Email Address, IP Address, User Agent (Browser/OS), Date/Time, Comment Content, and Content URL.'=>'<strong>评论</strong> - 用户发表的评论、电子邮箱地址、 IP 地址、用户代理（浏览器 / 操作系统）、日期 / 时间、评论内容和内容网址。','This screen is where you manage requests for an export of personal data.'=>'您可以在此界面管理个人数据导出请求。','Site URLs could not be switched to HTTPS.'=>'站点 URL 未能切换至 HTTPS。','Site URLs switched to HTTPS.'=>'站点 URL 已切换至 HTTPS。','It looks like HTTPS is not supported for your website at this point.'=>'看起来您的网站暂时不支持 HTTPS。','Sorry, you are not allowed to update this site to HTTPS.'=>'抱歉，您不能将该站点更新至 HTTPS。','Password reset links sent to %s user.'=>'密码重置链接已发送给 %s 位用户。','Password reset link sent.'=>'密码重置链接已发送。','Send %s a link to reset their password. This will not change their password, nor will it force a change.'=>'将链接发送给 %s 以重置其密码。本操作将不会修改其密码，也不会强制其修改密码。','Send Reset Link'=>'发送重置链接','Policies'=>'政策','The Privacy Settings require JavaScript.'=>'隐私设置需要 JavaScript 支持。','Privacy SettingsPolicy Guide'=>'隐私指南','Privacy SettingsSettings'=>'设置','Re-install version %s'=>'重新安装 %s 版本','Update to latest %s nightly'=>'升级至最新的 %s 每日