e used.'=>'如果您喜欢，您可以在此给您的分类和标签自定义 URL。比如，使用<code>topics</code>作为您的分类基础将会使您的分类链接变成<code>%s/topics/uncategorized/</code>。如果您留空此处，将使用默认值。','Release Lead'=>'版本发布负责人','Use the arrow buttons at the top of the dialog, or the left and right arrow keys on your keyboard, to navigate between media items quickly.'=>'使用对话框顶部的箭头按钮或键盘上的左右键，便能快速浏览媒体项目。','You can also delete individual items and access the extended edit screen from the details dialog.'=>'您也可以在此详情对话框中删除单个项目或访问扩展编辑界面。','Clicking an item will display an Attachment Details dialog, which allows you to preview media and make quick edits. Any changes you make to the attachment details will be automatically saved.'=>'点选一个项目将会带出「附件详情」对话框，您可在其中预览媒体并快速做出修改。您在「附件详情」对话框中做出的所有修改都会自动保存。','To delete media items, click the Bulk Select button at the top of the screen. Select any items you wish to delete, then click the Delete Selected button. Clicking the Cancel Selection button takes you back to viewing your media.'=>'要删除媒体项目，点击顶部的「批量选择」按钮，选择您想要删除的项目，再点击「删除所选」按钮。如您想返回查阅媒体，请点击「取消选择」按钮。','You can view your media in a simple visual grid or a list with columns. Switch between these views using the icons to the left above the media.'=>'您可以简单的网格视图或列表视图两种方式来查阅您的媒体文件。您可以使用媒体文件列表左上侧的图标来切换这些视图。','All the files you&#8217;ve uploaded are listed in the Media Library, with the most recent uploads listed first.'=>'您上传的所有文件都在「媒体库」界面中按上传时间顺序列出，最新上传的显示在最前面。','If you just want to get an idea of what&#8217;s available, you can browse Featured and Popular plugins by using the links above the plugins list. These sections rotate regularly.'=>'若您只想知道有什么插件可以选择，您可从列表上方的「特色」、「热门」中浏览。这些内容定期更新。','Browse Plugins'=>'浏览插件','Add Plugins'=>'安装插件','The %1$s constant in your %2$s file is no longer needed.'=>'在您的 %2$s 文件中的 %1$s 常量已不需要。','Invalid translation type.'=>'无效的翻译类型。','Welcome to the famous five-minute WordPress installation process! Just fill in the information below and you&#8217;ll be on your way to using the most extendable and powerful personal publishing platform in the world.'=>'欢迎使用著名的 WordPress 五分钟安装程序！请简单地填写下面的表单，来开始使用这个世界上最具扩展性、最强大的个人发布平台。','<strong>Compatible</strong> with your version of WordPress'=>'该插件<strong>兼容</strong>于您当前使用的 WordPress 版本','<strong>Incompatible</strong> with your version of WordPress'=>'该插件<strong>不兼容</strong>于您当前使用的 WordPress 版本','%d star'=>'%d 星','Select bulk action'=>'选择批量操作','Add the user without sending an email that requires their confirmation'=>'不发送确认邮件，直接添加用户。','The grid view for the Media Library requires JavaScript. <a href="%s">Switch to the list view</a>.'=>'媒体库的网格视图需要 JavaScript 支持。<a href="%s">切换回列表视图</a>。','Contributors'=>'贡献者','Donate to this plugin &#187;'=>'捐助该插件 &#187;','Plugin installer section titleReviews'=>'评价','The WordPress team is willing to help you. Forward this email to %s and the team will work with you to make sure your site is working.'=>'WordPress 团队愿意帮您。转发此邮件到 %s，我们的团队将协助您保持站点正常运作。','themesRecently Updated'=>'最近更新','Number/count of itemsCount'=>'总数','More Details'=>'更多详情','Plugin installer group titleTools'=>'工具','Plugin installer group titleSocial'=>'社交','Plugin installer group titlePerformance'=>'性能','Plugin InstallerBeta Testing'=>'Beta 测试','%s failed to embed.'=>'嵌入 %s 失败。','Filtering by:'=>'筛选条件：','Displayed on attachment pages.'=>'在附件页显示。','You can edit the image while preserving the thumbnail. For example, you may wish to have a square thumbnail that displays just a section of the image.'=>'您可以编辑图片，并不会影响缩略图。比如，您可能希望有一张只展示图片一部分的方形缩略图。','Once you have made your selection, you can adjust it by entering the size in pixels. The minimum selection size is the thumbnail size as set in the Media settings.'=>'您做出选择后，选区大小可以通过输入像素值来调整。最小值为媒体设置中指定的缩略图大小。','The aspect ratio is the relationship between the width and height. You can preserve the aspect ratio by holding down the shift key while resizing your selection. Use the input box to specify the aspect ratio, e.g. 1:1 (square), 4:3, 16:9, etc.'=>'纵横比是宽与高之间的比值。您可以通过在修改选区时按住 Shift 键来固定纵横比。使用输入框来指定纵横比，如 1:1（方形）、 4:3 、 16:9 等。','To crop the image, click on it and drag to make your selection.'=>'要裁切此图片，点击并拖动来确认您的选择。','You can proportionally scale the original image. For best results, scaling should be done before you crop, flip, or rotate. Images can only be scaled down, not up.'=>'您可以成比例地拉伸原始图片，在诸如裁切、旋转的编辑操作之前，最好先伸缩调整好您的图片尺寸。图片仅能被缩小，不能被放大。','Keyboard users: When you are working in the visual editor, you can use %s to access the toolbar.'=>'致键盘用户：在使用可视化编辑器时，可以使用 %s 访问工具栏。','A red bar on the left means the comment is waiting for you to moderate it.'=>'评论左侧的红条提示代表着该条评论正等待您的审核。','All comment types'=>'全部评论类型','themesLatest'=>'最新','themesPopular'=>'热门','themesFeatured'=>'特色','Attribute all content to:'=>'将这些内容的作者修改为：','Delete all content.'=>'删除所有内容。','What should be done with content owned by this user?'=>'如何处理该用户名下的内容？','<strong>Delete</strong> brings you to the Delete Users screen for confirmation, where you can permanently remove a user from your site and delete their content. You can also delete multiple users at once by using bulk actions.'=>'「<strong>删除</strong>」链接会带您到「删除用户」确认页面。在确认页面，您可以永久从站点中删除用户，并决定是否保留他们的内容。您也可以通过批量操作功能一次删除多个用户。','<strong>Remove</strong> allows you to remove a user from your site. It does not delete their content. You can also remove multiple users at once by using bulk actions.'=>'点击「<strong>移除</strong>」可以将用户从您的站点中移除。该操作不会删除用户之前所发布的内容。您也可以通过批量操作功能一次移除多个用户。','themeDetails &amp; Preview'=>'详情及预览','Search themes...'=>'搜索主题…','Search Themes'=>'搜索主题','Add Themes'=>'安装主题','https://wordpress.org/support/forum/how-to-and-troubleshooting'=>'https://cn.wordpress.org/support/forum/issues/','<strong>At a Glance</strong> &mdash; Displays a summary of the content on your site and identifies which theme and version of WordPress you are using.'=>'<strong>概览</strong>——显示您站点上的内容概况，以及主题与 WordPress 程序的版本信息。','<strong>Box Controls</strong> &mdash; Click the title bar of the box to expand or collapse it. Some boxes added by plugins may have configurable content, and will show a &#8220;Configure&#8221; link in the title bar if you hover over it.'=>'<strong>管理模块</strong>——点击模块的标题栏即可展开或收起它。另外，有些模块提供额外的配置选项，在您将鼠标移动到这些模块的标题栏上方时，会出现「配置」链接。','Sorry, you are not allowed to resume this theme.'=>'抱歉，您不能恢复此主题。','Edit date and time'=>'编辑日期和时间','Browse revisions'=>'浏览修订版本','Edit visibility'=>'编辑可见性','Edit status'=>'编辑状态','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/forum/multisite/">Support forums</a>'=>'<a href="https://cn.wordpress.org/support/forum/issues/multisite/">支持论坛</a>','Thank you for creating with <a href="%s">WordPress</a>.'=>'感谢使用 <a href="%s">WordPress</a> 进行创作。','Search installed themes...'=>'搜索已安装主题…','<strong>Translations</strong> &mdash; The files translating WordPress into your language are updated for you whenever any other updates occur. But if these files are out of date, you can <strong>click the &#8220;Update Translations&#8221;</strong> button.'=>'<strong>翻译</strong>——包含 WordPress 翻译的文件将在任何其他升级执行时一并被升级。如果这些文件已过时，您可以<strong>点击「更新翻译」</strong>按钮。','In most cases, WordPress will automatically apply maintenance and security updates in the background for you.'=>'在大多数情况下，WordPress 会在后台自动为您应用维护和安全更新。','<strong>WordPress</strong> &mdash; Updating your WordPress installation is a simple one-click procedure: just <strong>click on the &#8220;Update now&#8221; button</strong> when you are notified that a new version is available.'=>'<strong>WordPress</strong>——更新 WordPress 只需轻点一次鼠标。当有新版本可用时，<strong>点击「立即更新」按钮</strong>。','If an update is available, you&#8127;ll see a notification appear in the Toolbar and navigation menu.'=>'如果更新可用，您将会在工具栏和导航菜单处看到通知。','<strong>Themes and Plugins</strong> &mdash; To update individual themes or plugins from this screen, use the checkboxes to make your selection, then <strong>click on the appropriate &#8220;Update&#8221; button</strong>. To update all of your themes or plugins at once, you can check the box at the top of the section to select all before clicking the update button.'=>'<strong>主题和插件</strong>——要在本页面更新主题和插件，使用复选框选择要升级的项目，并<strong>点击对应的「更新」</strong>。选择「主题」区域和「插件」区域最上方的复选框以全选。','On this screen, you can update to the latest version of WordPress, as well as update your themes, plugins, and translations from the WordPress.org repositories.'=>'在这个界面中，您可以将 WordPress 更新至最新版，也可以从 WordPress.org 代码库升级您的主题、插件和翻译。','If you would like to see more themes to choose from, click on the &#8220;Add New Theme&#8221; button and you will be able to browse or search for additional themes from the <a href="%s">WordPress Theme Directory</a>. Themes in the WordPress Theme Directory are designed and developed by third parties, and are compatible with the license WordPress uses. Oh, and they&#8217;re free!'=>'若您希望从更多主题中选择，请点击「安装主题」按钮。切换到「安装主题」界面后，您就可以在<a href="%s">WordPress.org 主题目录</a>中浏览或搜索主题。 WordPress 主题目录中的主题是由第三方设计开发的，且与 WordPress 所用的版权许可证相兼容。最棒的是，它们都是免费的！','%1$s MB (%2$s%%) Space Used'=>'已使用 %1$s MB（%2$s%%）存储空间','%s MB Space Allowed'=>'允许使用 %s MB 存储空间','M jS'=>'n 月 j 日','%s Page'=>'%s 个页面','%s Post'=>'%s 篇文章','When this setting is in effect, a reminder is shown in the At a Glance box of the Dashboard that says, &#8220;Search engines discouraged&#8221;, to remind you that you have directed search engines to not crawl your site.'=>'当该项设置生效时，仪表盘中的「概况」模块将提醒您「自动建议搜索引擎不抓取」。您的站点在屏蔽搜索引擎期间无法被搜索引擎收录。','At a Glance'=>'概览','themeActive:'=>'已启用：','Accessibility Ready'=>'无障碍友好','This is a child theme of %s.'=>'这是 %s 的子主题。','When previewing on smaller monitors, you can use the collapse icon at the bottom of the left-hand pane. This will hide the pane, giving you more room to preview your site in the new theme. To bring the pane back, click on the collapse icon again.'=>'在小屏幕设备上预览时，您可点击左下方的「隐藏控制区」图标，便可收起边栏，以便留出更多空间显示新主题的外观。再次点击该图标，边栏将展开。','The theme being previewed is fully interactive &mdash; navigate to different pages to see how the theme handles posts, archives, and other page templates. The settings may differ depending on what theme features the theme being previewed supports. To accept the new settings and activate the theme all in one step, click the Activate &amp; Publish button above the menu.'=>'当前预览的主题是可互动的——您可以点击不同的页面来查看主题如何显示文章、存档和其他页面模板。根据主题所支持功能不同，您可以调整的项目也不同。要应用您在实时预览界面的设置，请点击左上角的「启用并发布」按钮。','Tap or hover on any theme then click the Live Preview button to see a live preview of that theme and change theme options in a separate, full-screen view. You can also find a Live Preview button at the bottom of the theme details screen. Any installed theme can be previewed and customized in this way.'=>'轻触或悬浮在任何已安装的主题上，然后点击下方的「实时预览」链接来查看实时预览，并在单独的界面预览并调整主题设置。您也可在主题详情界面的最底找到「实时预览」按钮。任何已安装的主题都可通过此方式预览及自定义。','The active theme is displayed highlighted as the first theme.'=>'当前主题作为第一个主题高亮显示。','Click Customize for the active theme or Live Preview for any other theme to see a live preview'=>'点击当前主题的自定义按钮或其他主题的实时预览按钮来查看实时预览','Click on the theme to see the theme name, version, author, description, tags, and the Delete link'=>'点击主题以查看主题名称、版本、作者、说明、标签和删除链接','Hover or tap to see Activate and Live Preview buttons'=>'轻触或将鼠标放在已安装的主题上，便会显示「启用」及「实时预览」按钮','This screen is used for managing your installed themes. Aside from the default theme(s) included with your WordPress installation, themes are designed and developed by third parties.'=>'此界面用于管理您已安装的主题。除了 WordPress 自带的默认主题之外，其他主题均是由第三方设计及开发的。','To activate a widget drag it to a sidebar or click on it. To deactivate a widget and delete its settings, drag it back.'=>'要启用某一小工具，将它拖动到侧栏或点击它。要禁用某一小工具并删除其设置，将它拖回来。','%s rating'=>'%s 个评级','%1$s rating based on %2$s rating'=>'%1$s 星（基于 %2$s 个评级）','This screen shows an individual user all of their sites in this network, and also allows that user to set a primary site. They can use the links under each site to visit either the front end or the dashboard for that site.'=>'本页面向用户展示他们在本站点网络中拥有的全部站点。用户可以设置一个主站点。用户可以使用站点名称下方的链接来访问站点的前端或仪表盘。','Error: [%1$s] %2$s'=>'错误：[%1$s] %2$s','Rollback Error: [%1$s] %2$s'=>'回滚错误：[%1$s] %2$s','The following translations failed to update