。','You can hide/display columns based on your needs and decide how many posts to list per screen using the Screen Options tab.'=>'您可在「显示选项」中依据您的需要隐藏或显示每页显示的文章数量。','You can customize the display of this screen in a number of ways:'=>'您可以通过以下方法来自定义本页面：','Search Installed Plugins'=>'搜索已安装插件','Your theme supports one menu. Select which menu you would like to use.'=>'您的主题支持一个菜单，请选择您希望使用的菜单。','Your theme does not support navigation menus or widgets.'=>'您的主题不支持导航菜单或小工具。','Categories and Tags Converter'=>'分类与标签转换器','Most Recent'=>'最近','Start date:'=>'开始日期：','Theme InstallerTag'=>'标签','Plugin InstallerTag'=>'标签','verbClear'=>'不排序','commentMark as spam'=>'标记为垃圾评论','Remove Background Image'=>'移除背景图片','Comments on &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'《%s》上的评论','Show advanced menu properties'=>'显示高级菜单属性','You have version %1$s installed. Update to %2$s.'=>'您正在使用的是版本 %1$s。升级至 %2$s。','Enabled'=>'启用','commentNot Spam'=>'不是垃圾评论','This will restore the original background image. You will not be able to restore any customizations.'=>'这将恢复原始背景图图片。您将无法还原任何自定义元素。','WordPress Blog'=>'WordPress 博客','Remove Users from Site'=>'从站点移除用户','&mdash; No role for this site &mdash;'=>'—这个站点没有任何用户角色—','New WordPress Site'=>'新 WordPress 站点','My Site'=>'我的站点','Sorry, you are not allowed to create posts or drafts on this site.'=>'抱歉，您不能在此站点上创建文章或草稿。','Sorry, you are not allowed to create pages on this site.'=>'抱歉，您不能在此站点上创建页面。','Custom site suspended message.'=>'自定义「站点挂起」消息。','Custom site inactive message.'=>'自定义「站点未激活」消息。','Custom site deleted message.'=>'自定义「站点已删除」消息。','If you have posts or comments in another system, WordPress can import those into this site. To get started, choose a system to import from below:'=>'若有需要，您可以把其他系统的文章和评论内容导入到这个 WordPress 站点。请从以下系统中选择一个导入源，开始导入：','No items.'=>'无项目。','To use a subdomain configuration, you must have a wildcard entry in your DNS. This usually means adding a %s hostname record pointing at your web server in your DNS configuration tool.'=>'要使用子域名配置，您的 DNS 中必须拥有一条通配符记录。这